---
// Landing hero — ported from hero-plus-features-v2.html
// (.mbv-herowrap / .mbv-hero / .mbv-doc / .mbv-feats).
// Subhead uses the expanded copy from the design spec.
// CTA links to the Mac App Store (app shipped).
---

<div class="mbv-herowrap">
  <div class="mbv-hero">
    <div>
      <div class="mbv-titlerow">
        <img class="mbv-ico" src="/icon.png" width="84" height="84" alt="Markdown Better View app icon" />
        <h1 class="mbv-h1">See <code>Markdown</code> as it’s meant to look.</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="mbv-sub">Extremely fast — opens and renders documents instantly. Universal binary — native on Apple Silicon and Intel. Themes, live reload, table of contents, instant find, Quick Look.</p>

      <a class="mbv-cta" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6773928994" target="_blank" rel="noopener">⌘ Get it on the Mac App Store</a>

      <span class="mbv-note">Universal · macOS 15+ · sandboxed · no tracking</span>
    </div>

    <div class="mbv-doc">
      <div class="dh1">Release Notes</div>
      <p>Open a file and it just renders — beautifully, instantly.</p>
      <blockquote>“Rendered, not raw.”</blockquote>
      <div class="codeblk"><span class="c"># swift</span><br /><span class="k">let</span> joy = <span class="s">"GFM tables, math, mermaid"</span></div>
      <ul>
        <li>Live reload on save</li>
        <li>Five themes · dark mode</li>
      </ul>
      <hr />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mbv-feats">
    <span>Live reload</span>
    <span>Themes + dark</span>
    <span>Table of contents</span>
    <span>Find</span>
    <span>Quick Look</span>
    <span>Folder → tabs</span>
    <span>Export PDF</span>
  </div>
</div>
